Module java.desktop
Package java.awt

Class Canvas.AccessibleAWTCanvas

java.lang.Object
javax.accessibility.AccessibleContext
java.awt.Component.AccessibleAWTComponent
java.awt.Canvas.AccessibleAWTCanvas
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, AccessibleComponent
Enclosing class:
Canvas
protected class Canvas.AccessibleAWTCanvas
extends Component.AccessibleAWTComponent
This class implements accessibility support for the Canvas class. It provides an implementation of the Java Accessibility API appropriate to canvas user-interface elements.
Since:
1.3
